org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.css

Class CSSTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.antlr.runtime.BaseRecognizer
      • org.antlr.runtime.tree.TreeParser
        • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.css.CSSTree

  • public class CSSTree
extends org.antlr.runtime.tree.TreeParser
    This is a tree grammar for advanced CSS in Flex. It walks the AST generated by the CSS parser and builds CSS DOM objects.
